  "title": "Aures - Sea Dwellers",
  "description": "Underwater villages and sea traders with random generation. Vanilla style.",
  "body": "Curseforge - https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/nocubes-sea-dwellers\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><br><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/867/18/ima1244564353ge.png\" alt=\"\"></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Welcome to RealmRPG, a mod series featuring vanilla-like medieval fantasy additions!</strong></span><br><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Sea Dwellers</strong> mod adds bizzare fish-like traders and underwater villages, but without going too far from original game style and balance.&nbsp;<br></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1270/857/newcanvas332342321312-png.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"597\" height=\"423\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br><strong>Features</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>12 sea traders</strong> with unique goods.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>60+ structures</strong> that diversify the empty ocean.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>30+ new items</strong> to enhance your underwater exploration experience.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>~10 quests</strong> from the <strong>ocean dragon</strong>, which will be difficult to complete without detailed exploration.</span></li>\n<li>New underwater culture - <strong>mussels</strong></li>\n<li>5 new types of food</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1271/7/ocean_dragon3-gif.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"633\" height=\"600\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1270/957/11111111111-png.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #f00;\"><strong>Warning</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #f00;\">All versions above 3.0.0 (Minecraft 1.18 and above) require <a style=\"color: #f00;\" href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/geckolib\" rel=\"nofollow\">GeckoLib</a>.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #f00;\">Animations don't work with shaders? Disable Entity Shadows in shader settings.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1270/956/111111111112-png.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\"></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Configuration &amp; Recommendations<br></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">This mod by default should work good alongside any other mods installed. While there is no classic config file, you still can customize many features by creating a simple datapack with tags yourself.&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</li>\n<li>The spawn of wild mermorphs is configured using placed_feature.</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Special compatibility with FarmersDelight, Aquaculture, BiomesWeHaveGone, Regions Unexplored, Terralith.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Old info about mod <a href=\"https://github.com/BlackAures1/SeaDwellersWiki/wiki\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">here.</a></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1270/955/11111111111222-png.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\"></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Permissions &amp; FAQ</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">You are allowed to use this mod in your videos and modpacks as long as credited and download link leads here.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">You are not allowed to use content of this mod (textures, models, etc) in your projects.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">You are not allowed re-upload this mod to other websites and launchers.&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Fabric or backports of new features ARE NOT PLANNED!</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Bug reports and re-balance ideas are welcome.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1270/958/111111111112222-png.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1344\" height=\"756\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Credits<br></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Mod authors -<strong> NoCube, Black Aures</strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Made with -<strong> MCreator, Blockbench, PaintNet</strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Inspired by<strong> - Luca, Creature from the Black Lagoon, Lovecraftian creatures.</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;More Realm RPG mods:<br></span><br><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/nocubes-sea-dwellers\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/891/22/638332229090166009.png\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"></a><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/realm-rpg-creep-crop\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/895/730/638340578799643798.png\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"></a><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/realm-rpg-imps-demons\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/886/558/638323109380204126.png\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"></a><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/realm-rpg-dragon-wyrms\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/872/792/638291974755181770.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"></a><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/realm-rpg-fallen-adventurers\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/882/139/638313378229849817.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"></a><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/pots-and-mimics-rpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/847/493/638246901123812282.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"></a></strong></span><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/gothic-rpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/851/851/638254279369665236.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"></strong></a></span></p>",
